ezdb.serde
Class VersionedSerde<O>

java.lang.Object
  ezdb.serde.VersionedSerde<O>
Type Parameters:
O - The type of object that we wish to version.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serde<VersionedSerde.Versioned<O>>
public class VersionedSerde<O>
extends Object
implements Serde<VersionedSerde.Versioned<O>>

A wrapper serde that handles pre-pending some version number to a byte payload. The format for the version byte array is: 

 [4 byte version]
 [arbitrary object bytes]

Author:
criccomini
